latestPosts.caption:
A new year marks a new beginning, and with it comes a new bike and a fresh season. I had a wonderful experience at the recent rally, riding the all-new Xpulse 210. The bike feels completely different from the Xpulse 200 4V, and it was exciting to explore its capabilities.

There is still a lot to learn and improve upon, but I’m happy with the progress so far. I managed to secure 4th place in my class, and I’m determined to push my limits even further in the next race.

A big thank you to @heromotosports for the support and for giving me the opportunity to grow and compete at this level.
